Name: Wampee Helicopters
About the game: Wampee Helicopters about the Game Wampee Helicopters Is 3D action game, part 3D platformer/shoot em up, involving Helicopters and blasting your way to the goal. 21 action packed levels, a large variety of enemies. The inspiration of this game was from early 3D video games of the mid 90’s. The Goal was to make a 3D game based on the limitations early 3D video games had, with a retro based soundtrack, and 90’s Art style. Genre, 3D action/ 3d platformer/3rd person shooter A game based on flight Low poly 3D environment
